column5: Hey Guys, Anybody been to Sabaskong in the last week, thinking about heading up this weekend. I know "Greenhorn" was up a week or two ago, but I havn't seen a post upon his return. Thanks Eric
JUST GOT BACK SUNDAY. SNOW AND COLD, 2 DAYS CAUGHT NUMBERS OF CRAPPIE AND WALLEYE, 2 DAYS COLD FRONTS SHUT THEM DOWN. THEY ARE DEEP, 35-40 FT ON THE BOTTOM IN USUAL AREAS. 45 DEGREE WATER TEMP.
